{"tid":785723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】759阿信屋老闆林偉駿逝世","createTime":"2018-08-19T12:20:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T12:40:34.000Z","uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"978c7d72633e3c20163d5726789b914428190954","tid":785723,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T12:20:09.000Z","msg":"CEC國際控股（759）有限公司發公告表示，759阿信屋創辦人兼主席林偉駿昨日於在養和醫院逝世。<br />\n<br />\n公司董事會將盡力按已故主席訂立的策略繼續經營集團之業務。將重組其架構，並適時刊發進一步公告。<br />\n<br />\n公告未有透露其逝世原因。"},{"pid":"5e4209b73a9a20c69b77fc979d43e06419de0141","tid":785723,"uid":74598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T12:20:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e13056d5ae56e5da1ec2f496b514282f5bd8b950","tid":785723,"uid":166597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T12:20:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nr.i.p"},{"pid":"53315e924cf6f3e32a09bb5155f757aa380c36ad","tid":785723,"uid":82398,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T12:20:53.000Z","msg":"759 1折優惠 做帛金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c25ba0e68f065737629311f2c5adaad420fe0e","tid":785723,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T12:21:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7495b98c866ceea7bff87bac2018fc50dc6138a1","tid":785723,"uid":106363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T12:24:37.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"ff3a3161b992c76152e0e7cbf1b939e61c579587","tid":785723,"uid":5278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T12:33:23.000Z","msg":"咁突然"},{"pid":"d943d152e8d8e477bdbac5569f7d6842d0b86054","tid":785723,"uid":106363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T12:35:09.000Z","msg":"【事出突然】759阿信屋老闆林偉駿逝世　<br />\n【事出突然】759阿信屋老闆林偉駿逝世<br />\n<br />\nCEC國際控股（759）有限公司發公告表示，759阿信屋創辦人兼主席林偉駿昨日於在養和醫院逝世。<br />\n<br />\n公司董事會將盡力按已故主席訂立的策略繼續經營集團之業務。將重組其架構，並適時刊發進一步公告。公告未有透露其逝世原因。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者今年6月1日下午曾於養和醫院內分泌及糖尿病中心碰見林偉駿，當時他身穿便服，站在接待處前等候。養和醫院網站資料顯示，該中心專為糖尿及內分泌疾病患者提供一站式治療及護理服務，駐場醫護包括糖尿病專科醫生，還有糖尿病專科護士和足病診療師等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180819&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58583418\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180819%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58583418&d=q6sYCdTlnVntpQwkAG5Zb6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=a95b49f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180819%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58583418&h=e0e7ff00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180819&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58583418</a><br />\n<br />\nsent by HK News 香港新聞報紙:<a href=\"http://goo.gl/Vn18QN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FVn18QN&d=q6sYCdTlnVntpQwkAG5Zb6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=65c31f91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">goo.gl/Vn18QN</a>"},{"pid":"16288eb218ad85b99c64b7d9bee791a0ae049645","tid":785723,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T12:40:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2140000/2141379/759_thumb_20180819_K_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2140000%2F2141379%2F759_thumb_20180819_K_1024.jpg&h=54870659&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}